  dialogueBubble: {fileID: 367139716}
  dialogueText: {fileID: 1593928034}
  finalMessages:
  - Wake up.
  - Those weren't cupcakes... they were your friends. Real people.
  - The drugs twisted everything, made you see sweetness where there was only horror.
  - Every swing of that hammer, every point you earned... you destroyed the people
    you cared about.
  - "This is what it does\u2014it blinds you to reality until it's too late, and
    there's no going back."
